<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<module moduleId="IlluminatedTactileSwitch12_7mm_with_support_631e09" fritzingVersion="1.0.6">
 <version>4</version>
 <author>Lisa Chyhryna</author>
 <title>Illuminated Tact LED Switch 12.7mm with supports</title>
 <label>TSL</label>
 <date>2023-07-30</date>
 <history date="2023-07-30" author="Kjell Morgenstern">Added support holes</history>
 <history date="2023-08-05" author="Kjell Morgenstern">Recalculate viewBox. Change pin distances to multiples of 2.54mm</history>
 <history date="2026-02-15" author="Kjell Morgenstern">Add CX marker. Resize schematic connectors. Add a Fritzing version</history>
 <tags>
  <tag>switch</tag>
  <tag>LED</tag>
  <tag>Button</tag>
  <tag>Tactile</tag>
 </tags>
 <properties>
  <property name="family">Tactile button</property>
  <property name="hole size">1.2mm</property>
  <property name="part number">TSL12121</property>
 </properties>
 <taxonomy>tactile.switch.led</taxonomy>
 <url> http://www.khan.cn/en/productshow/TSL12121 </url>
 <description>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd"&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name="qrichtext" content="1" /&gt;&lt;style type="text/css"&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=" font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:8.25pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;"&gt;
This version of the tactile switch comes with support pins for additional stability. The footprint was modified to 0.1inch factors for better alignment.
&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Travel&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;0.25mmР’В±0.1mm&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Rated load&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;DC 12V 50mA&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Contact Resistance&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;≤100mΩ&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Dielectric Strength&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;AC 250V for 1 minute&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Insulation Resistance&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt; ≥100MΩ&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Electrical Life&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;≥100,000 cycles&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;/tr&gt;    
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</description>
